CardanoBudzH1EpicPlusWinner.name: CardanoBudz Epic+ Winner
details: You are the lucky recipient of a Cardano Budz
Epic+ Token.  You have been issued a redeemable
token for a real world prize.  Please contact us
at winner@nftatelier.io.  We will provide a list of
available prizes that you can redeem with this token.
You must be over the age of 21, and a legal USA
resident.  If you do not meet this criteria, you may
pass this token to someone who does meet that criteria.
We will verify eligibility requirements, and have you
return this token in exchange for the real world item.
The token must be redeemed within 30 days of it being
first sent to the winning payment address.
